channel.title: I need a blank client for my server or help with eclipse 639
channel.description: My server is a 639 I have portforwarded, and I sent my client to my friends via email. (the client has my ip as the ip it's supposed to connect to.) but when they try to open the client (eclipse 639) all they get is a command prompt that shows up for like a half a second and leaves. then nothing else happens. So I'm hoping that you guys can help me out as far as finding out how i can get my friends on my server, or where I can find a blank 639 Client. Like the ones where you type in the IP you want to connect to in a little box. In this case (Duphascape.no-ip.biz) ____________________________ [___Please enter an IP below___] [____[[u]Duphascape.no-ip.biz[/u]]____] [___________________________]
